import React from 'react'
import Background from '../components/Background'
import Logo from '../components/Logo'
import Header from '../components/Header'
import Paragraph from '../components/Paragraph'
import BackButton from '../components/BackButton'
import Button from '../components/Button'
import VerticalTopToButtomWraper from '../components/VerticalTopToButtomWraper'
import { View, Text } from 'react-native'
import MessengeHeader from '../containers/MessengeHeader'
import Footer from '../components/Footer'
import { Title, Appbar } from 'react-native-paper';
import { Platform } from 'react-native';
const MORE_ICON = Platform.OS === 'ios' ? 'dots-horizontal' : 'dots-vertical';

export default function Dashboard({ navigation }) {
  return (
    <Background>
      <VerticalTopToButtomWraper>
      {/* <BackButton goBack={navigation.goBack} /> */}
      <Appbar.Header>
          <Appbar.Content title="Title" subtitle={'Subtitle'} />
          <Appbar.Action icon="magnify" onPress={() => {}} />
          <Appbar.Action icon={MORE_ICON} onPress={() => {}} />
      </Appbar.Header>
      <Header>
        <Title >Family Members</Title >
        <Text>Hello 323</Text>
      </Header>
      <MessengeHeader>
        <Text>Hello 2121</Text>
        <Text>Hello 323</Text>
      </MessengeHeader>
        <Text>Hello 11</Text>
        <Text>Hello 22</Text>
        <Button
          mode="outlined"
          onPress={() =>
            navigation.reset({
              index: 0,
              routes: [{ name: 'StartScreen' }],
            })
          }
        >
          Logout
        </Button>
        <Footer>
          <Text>Hello 33</Text>
          <Text>Hello 33</Text>
          <Text>Hello 33</Text>
          <Text>Hello 33</Text>
        </Footer>
      </VerticalTopToButtomWraper>
    </Background>
  )
}
